        <source>xCM_ReserveSelection(_features : CMIF_ExternalDBFeatureSet input) updating;
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
//19/01/2017 		cnwrh7		TFS	2929  Additional Fields Required (CM_ReserveSelection/CM_ReserveTI) in SQL Native for Release Requests
// 13 Mar 2017	cnwrs1		TFS3648 add other Release Request fields
//19/07/2022	navtnr20	ChangeRequest 53974: EUP - OUT - Additional Fields on Release Line Level	
//12 July 2023	navmv20	CR 58420 Task 58421: Jade - Data Extra JRW Views																
*/

